00:35:47,520 --> 00:35:48,520
You are insane.

495
00:35:50,520 --> 00:35:51,520
Why notjust kill me?

496
00:35:52,200 --> 00:35:53,200
Because, Jim...

497
00:35:54,160 --> 00:35:56,231
I need you at the head of the GCPD.

498
00:35:56,840 --> 00:35:58,831
- I need...
- Someone you can control.

499
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:03,069
You've been planning this
since the day we first met.

500
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:07,110
This isn't about Gotham.
This is revenge.

501
00:36:08,120 --> 00:36:09,554
For me killing Mario.

502
00:36:15,640 --> 00:36:16,960
(GUN THUDS)

503
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:20,795
You want
to arrest me, arrest me.

504
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,589
But I will talk.

505
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:30,115
And the cops that died,
the friend that you betrayed,

506
00:36:30,200 --> 00:36:31,838
will all have been for nothing.

507
00:36:34,040 --> 00:36:35,792
The GCPD will crumble.

508
00:36:37,040 --> 00:36:38,599
Penguin, or someone worse,

509
00:36:38,680 --> 00:36:42,469
will take over
and you will lose Gotham forever.

510
00:36:45,040 --> 00:36:48,795
Or, take on the sin as your own.

511
00:36:51,080 --> 00:36:53,993
Keep the GCPD.
Let them think you're a hero.

512
00:36:54,560 --> 00:36:57,632
But live knowing who you are.
What you've done.

513
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:01,118
That's my revenge.

514
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:08,920
(PHONE BEEPS)

515
00:37:13,520 --> 00:37:14,749
FEMALE OFFICER: GCPD.

516
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:18,192
<i>GCPD, how can I help you?</i>

517
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:22,275
<i>Hello? Anyone there? Anybody?</i>

518
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:23,634
This is Gordon.

519
00:37:24,640 --> 00:37:26,551
I'm at Sofia Falcone's...

520
00:37:28,720 --> 00:37:30,358
Ijust shot and killed the Pyg.

521
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:47,392
Oh, thank Christ. You're safe.

522
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:51,199
Master Bruce, listen,
I don't want to fight anymore.

523
00:37:53,240 --> 00:37:54,240
You win.

524
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:57,638
If this is how you want to deal

525
00:37:57,720 --> 00:37:59,496
with what you've been going through,
then so be it.

526
00:37:59,520 --> 00:38:00,919
I'm not gonna try and stop you.

527
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:03,960
Butjust knowthis...

528
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:07,999
You will remember who you are,

529
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:10,310
and when you do,
Iwill be right here...

530
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:12,676
No. you won't be.

531
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:16,635
I went to my lawyer and had him
draw up emancipation papers.

532
00:38:21,160 --> 00:38:22,639
You're no longer my legal guardian.

533
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:31,760
I won't sign them.

534
00:38:32,280 --> 00:38:35,636
You don't have to. Now I'm going out.

535
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:38,176
If you're still here when I get back,

536
00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:40,032
I'II go to the police
and show them my face.

537
00:38:43,240 --> 00:38:45,356
- Master Bruce, please...
- Alfred, you're fired.

538
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:49,233
Now get the hell out of my house.

539
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:56,271
(nooa CLOSES)

540
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:06,509
(PANTING)

541
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:11,392
Butch! Say something!

542
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:17,355
Say something.

543
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:21,795
(PIPE CLATTERS)

544
00:39:22,040 --> 00:39:23,189
(GROANS)

545
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:27,359
I'm sorry.

546
00:39:33,480 --> 00:39:34,709
I tried.

547
00:39:57,720 --> 00:39:59,074
(LAUGHING)

548
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:28,240
(INDISTINCT CHATFERING)

549
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:57,000
Harvey.

550
00:40:57,680 --> 00:40:59,717
I wasjust, uh, dropping something off.

551
00:41:00,880 --> 00:41:03,998
Oh, I heard you got the Pyg.

552
00:41:04,880 --> 00:41:06,314
- And Penguin.
- Yeah.

553
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:10,353
So everything turned out well.

554
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:13,512
- You didn't even need me...
- You got a second? Could we, uh...

555
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:19,956
They, uh, believe in you.
Don't let them down.

556
00:41:56,080 --> 00:41:57,479
What the hell happened to me?

557
00:42:02,200 --> 00:42:06,433
PENGUIN: Traitors.
Every single one of them.

558
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:11,915
I'II kill her! I will flay her alive!

559
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:16,036
Her and Gordon and Zsasz and...

560
00:42:16,120 --> 00:42:17,349
(BANGING)

561
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:19,511
- MAN: Hey, buddy...
- (GASPS)

562
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:24,870
- Do not talk to me.
- I get it, pal...

563
00:42:25,320 --> 00:42:27,994
This place is full of loonies.

564
00:42:28,640 --> 00:42:31,553
I just thought,
we could help each other out.

565
00:42:34,320 --> 00:42:37,551
And how can you help me? (CHUCKLES)

566
00:42:37,640 --> 00:42:44,194
Well, not to toot my own horn,
but I'm a very resourceful fellow.

567
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:47,318
So, toot. Toot, toot!

568
00:42:48,320 --> 00:42:49,674
(MAN CACKLES)

569
00:42:50,280 --> 00:42:51,395
(GASPS)

570
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:52,754
I know that laugh.

571
00:42:53,160 --> 00:42:56,551
What do you say, pal?
L'II be your best friend.

572
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:58,399
(GASPS)

573
00:43:00,280 --> 00:43:01,759
Give me a smile...

